        {
            "title": "日股初段跌逾350點　失守54000點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東京股市初段回吐。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數跌穿54000點，較早時報53983點，跌357點，跌0.66%。</p>\n</div>",
